---
title: BeaconLink Deployment Request Sequence
---

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as Platform Operator
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant Auth as Identity Provider
    participant Policy as Policy Engine
    participant Workflow as Workflow Engine
    participant Planner as Deployment Planner
    participant Scheduler as Distributed Scheduler
    participant Inventory as Inventory Service
    participant Relay as Relay Network
    participant Agent as BeaconLink Agent
    participant Runtime as Runtime Manager
    participant Adapter as Runtime Adapter
    participant Events as Event Streaming Platform
    participant Audit as Audit Service

    %% =====================================================
    %% Deployment Submission
    %% =====================================================

    User->>API: Submit deployment manifest

    API->>Auth: Authenticate request
    Auth-->>API: Identity verified

    API->>Policy: Authorize deployment
    Policy-->>API: Deployment permitted

    API->>Audit: Record deployment request

    %% =====================================================
    %% Workflow Creation
    %% =====================================================

    API->>Workflow: Create deployment workflow

    Workflow->>Planner: Build deployment plan

    Planner->>Inventory: Retrieve infrastructure inventory
    Inventory-->>Planner: Sites, agents, capabilities

    Planner->>Planner: Validate manifest
    Planner->>Planner: Resolve dependencies
    Planner->>Planner: Compute immutable revision

    Planner-->>Workflow: Execution plan

    %% =====================================================
    %% Scheduling
    %% =====================================================

    Workflow->>Scheduler: Request execution targets

    Scheduler->>Inventory: Query healthy agents
    Inventory-->>Scheduler: Available execution nodes

    Scheduler->>Policy: Evaluate placement policies
    Policy-->>Scheduler: Placement approved

    Scheduler-->>Workflow: Selected target agents

    %% =====================================================
    %% Deployment Dispatch
    %% =====================================================

    Workflow->>Relay: Dispatch deployment task

    Relay->>Agent: Deliver deployment

    Agent->>Agent: Validate desired state
    Agent->>Runtime: Prepare deployment

    Runtime->>Adapter: Translate deployment
    Adapter-->>Runtime: Runtime-specific plan

    %% =====================================================
    %% Runtime Execution
    %% =====================================================

    Runtime->>Adapter: Execute deployment

    loop Deployment Progress

        Adapter-->>Runtime: Progress update

        Runtime-->>Agent: Runtime status

        Agent->>Relay: Progress report

        Relay->>Workflow: Forward progress

        Workflow->>Events: Publish DeploymentProgress

    end

    %% =====================================================
    %% Deployment Completion
    %% =====================================================

    Adapter-->>Runtime: Deployment complete

    Runtime-->>Agent: Execution successful

    Agent->>Inventory: Update workload inventory

    Inventory-->>Workflow: Inventory synchronized

    Workflow->>Events: Publish DeploymentCompleted
    Workflow->>Audit: Record successful deployment

    Workflow-->>API: Deployment complete

    API-->>User: Deployment successful

    %% =====================================================
    %% Failure Handling
    %% =====================================================

    alt Deployment Failure

        Adapter-->>Runtime: Execution failed

        Runtime-->>Agent: Failure details

        Agent->>Workflow: Failure report

        Workflow->>Events: Publish DeploymentFailed

        Workflow->>Audit: Record deployment failure

        Workflow->>Planner: Request rollback

        Planner-->>Workflow: Rollback plan

        Workflow->>Relay: Dispatch rollback

    else Deployment Successful

        Note over User,Agent: Desired state converged.<br/>Continuous reconciliation<br/>maintains deployment health.

    end